my AD has been rejected please check

I'm sorry to hear that your ad was rejected. To help you better, could you please check your email for a message from adsupport@newsbreak.com? It should contain the specific reason for the rejection. Once you have that information, you can address the issue and resubmit your ad. If you believe the rejection was a mistake, you can appeal by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com. For more details on handling ad rejections, please refer to this article: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next).
